 It will create the appearance of completeness. And you won=E2=80=99t notic=
e until someone tries to act on the document and discovers half the informa=
tion is plausible fiction.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,=
55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">The best prompt in the world can=
=E2=80=99t overcome bad inputs. If you=E2=80=99re writing a project proposa=
