=E2=80=99re writing meeting notes and you don=E2=80=99t have the decisions =
documented, AI will infer from context. If you=E2=80=99re writing technical=
 documentation and the specs are vague, AI will make reasonable guesses.</p=
><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font=
-size: 16px;">This is dangerous because the output looks complete. It has t=
he right structure. It has the right tone. It passes all your quality check=
