=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16=
px;">The principle: before you prompt AI to write anything, you need to ver=
ify you have the actual information required. Not =E2=80=9CI sort of know t=
his=E2=80=9D but =E2=80=9CI have the specific data, decisions, examples I n=
eed.=E2=80=9D If you don=E2=80=99t, the prompt should be =E2=80=9Chelp me i=
dentify what information I=E2=80=99m missing=E2=80=9D not =E2=80=9Cwrite th=
e document.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55)=
;line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">This means the discipline happens befo=
re prompting. You need to know: what information does this document type re=
quire? Do I have it? If not, what questions do I need to answer first?</p><=
